('8af672bc-ce15-5d01-9ac1-7d07d0b04c29', 'e51ed3b7-5c32-4314-8a64-f4111856716d', 'The textbook focuses on basic ___ operations, such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.', '這本教科書著重於基礎的算術運算，例如加、減、乘、除。', 'arithmetic', 'geometric', 'algebraic', 'biological', '詞根 arithm- 源自希臘語，意為「數字」。', 'arithm (數字) + etic (形容詞字尾) → 處理數字的 → 算術的。', '2026-07-06 23:53:21', '2026-07-06 23:53:21'),
('49c88ae7-b4ea-55b8-a75a-27eb9f58c81d', 'c0b8ce19-5f2f-4763-b0b2-abca5ece3f48', 'To understand the problem fully, we must examine every ___ of the situation.', '為了充分了解這個問題，我們必須檢視情況的各個方面。', 'aspect', 'habit', 'season', 'height', 'aspect 源自拉丁語詞根 spec，意為「看」(to look)，指事物被觀察到的「面向」。', '聯想 spec 相關單字如 inspect (檢查) 或 spectator (觀眾)，aspect 就是觀察事物的「角度」或「方面」。', '2026-07-07 00:48:14', '2026-07-07 00:48:14'),
('80e0da55-e412-52ac-9c94-a1dd0dd82951', 'fabb9784-e257-4925-bb1c-c164fa62a341', 'After years of intense training and strict dieting, the young ___ finally won a gold medal at the Olympic Games.', '經過多年的高強度訓練和嚴格的飲食控制，這位年輕的運動員終於在奧運會上贏得了金牌。', 'athlete', 'doctor', 'artist', 'scientist', '字根 ath- 來自希臘語 athlos (意為競賽或苦難) + suffix -lete (指從事某種活動的人)。', '想像一個 ath(力)lete(人) → 很有力氣的人，也就是運動員。', '2026-07-07 01:45:58', '2026-07-07 01:45:58'),
