('b082a041-c8d7-5669-b455-6289eed3edd1', 'dfcc0bf8-5083-44a2-a5e1-ee7a81d5f096', 'Every summer, my brother goes to the stadium to watch a professional ___ game.', '每個夏天，我哥哥都會去球場看職業棒球比賽。', 'baseball', 'basketball', 'football', 'volleyball', 'base (基地/底座) + ball (球) → 棒球', '想像球員站在 base (壘包) 上玩 ball (球) 的運動。', '2026-07-10 07:58:45', '2026-07-10 07:58:45'),
