('c6632828-ade2-5941-b5da-f7408d898c09', 'a0f2450b-cd7d-4a67-9122-8fff7fb79991', 'After reading the scientific paper twice, the student still struggled to ___ the complex theories presented by the researcher.', '在讀了兩遍這篇科學論文後，學生仍然難以理解研究人員所提出的複雜理論。', 'comprehend', 'neglect', 'predict', 'maintain', 'com- (完全) + prehend (抓住) → 完整地抓住資訊 → 理解。', '聯想「抓取」的概念：把知識全部「抓」進腦袋裡，就是「理解」。', '2026-07-11 11:42:18', '2026-07-11 11:42:18'),
